org.obrel.core

Class RelationWrapper<T,R,F extends Function<R,T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.obrel.core.RelatedObject
      • org.obrel.core.SerializableRelatedObject
        • org.obrel.core.Relation<T>
          • org.obrel.core.RelationWrapper<T,R,F>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventHandler<RelationEvent<R>>, EventListener, java.io.Serializable, Relatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RelationAlias, RelationView

    public abstract class RelationWrapper<T,R,F extends Function<R,T>>
extends Relation<T>
implements EventHandler<RelationEvent<R>>
    A wrapper for other relations that provides a view of the relation with a different relation type and optionally a different datatype. Wrapper can also be set on a different parent than the wrapped relation.
    See Also:
